{"tid":1907571,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"【港產口罩】再有 Made in Hong Kong 口罩！「Savewo 救世」開發 5 款口罩","createTime":"2020-03-02T16:38:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T11:42:47.000Z","uid":85180,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1100d84c4b887cf9fb6512bf3a2746397386f4c5","tid":1907571,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T16:38:56.000Z","msg":"【港產口罩】再有 Made in Hong Kong 口罩！「Savewo 救世」開發 5 款口罩<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎（武漢肺炎）疫情持續於全球肆虐，口罩成為各國人民日常生活的必需品，但由於目前不少國家都有規限口罩出口，有機會導致香港的口罩供應隨時再次面臨不足。幸好香港亦有不少商家或好心人自發成立「Made in Hong Kong」的口罩，目前已有5 - 6 間港產口罩廠宣布成立，而近日再有一間名為「Savewo 救世」的口罩廠成立，並稱目前正在研發 5 項產品。<br />\n<br />\n香港再有「Made in Hong Kong」口罩商成立<br />\n「Savewo 救世」登場<br />\n目前正研發 5 項產品<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2575000/2578746/88175387_109318037341635_6380437723689254912_o_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2575000%2F2578746%2F88175387_109318037341635_6380437723689254912_o_600.jpg&h=189bdf46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據「Savewo 救世」於其 Facebook 專頁上指目前正在研發 5 款口罩，分別有可重用口罩、配搭重用口罩使用的濾綿、一次性 4 層口罩，以及對應 3M 6000 及 7000 系列呼吸器的氣密封蓋等。而且氣密封蓋現時已經進入開模具的步驟，希望可以取代 3D 打印，大量生產，務求可以做到香港製造的同時令更多用戶受惠！<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2575000/2578746/88273046_109318054008300_7785637966516322304_o_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2575000%2F2578746%2F88273046_109318054008300_7785637966516322304_o_600.jpg&h=045a590a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2575000/2578746/88183203_109318074008298_8041212477955899392_o_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2575000%2F2578746%2F88183203_109318074008298_8041212477955899392_o_600.jpg&h=1c533df8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2575000/2578746/88183283_109318110674961_5398865494134489088_o_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2575000%2F2578746%2F88183283_109318110674961_5398865494134489088_o_600.jpg&h=76affdcc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d12aa22e667dc90f0e2a26095ab15162acae805b","tid":1907571,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T05:03:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb89a21762781536ace1d0234d3783736e1f0769","tid":1907571,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T05:06:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/savewohk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsavewohk%2F&d=FoM%2FNT%2BxDvRLDdkWKwCN%2BG9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=9e586766\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/savewohk/</a>"},{"pid":"f28d222d1ce3fd35faf4167f89368ae3e14c054f","tid":1907571,"uid":190248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T13:27:12.000Z","msg":"岩岩見unwire有介紹<br />\n有無人知背景"},{"pid":"c04ab935884d3229001ea65809929dc1291f4cfd","tid":1907571,"uid":44725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T14:31:00.000Z","msg":"眾籌真係好易搵錢, 以前仙人都係整幾張網站圖, sale idea 就籌咗50萬<br />\n都係個句, 有誠意幫香港人就影D生產線/ 實物相黎俾人睇<br />\n無既一律當係眾籌陷阱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a16a0d6bb5a14b413da266a341e780763f61cbf9","tid":1907571,"uid":121610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1100d84c4b887cf9fb6512bf3a2746397386f4c5","tid":1907571,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T16:38:56.000Z","msg":"【港產口罩】再有 Made in Hong Kong 口罩！「Savewo 救世」開發 5 款口罩<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎（武漢肺炎）疫情持續於全球肆虐，口罩成為各國人民日常生活的必需